PHPBB & MDC
-----------

(based on http://viewvc.svn.mozilla.org/vc/addons/trunk/site/vendors/phpbb/)

This directory holds what you need to connect MDN to a phpbb instance.  Instructions:

0) Install phpBB following their docs/INSTALL.html 
0.1) Remove install directory once install is complete.

1) Copy auth_mdc.php to /includes/auth/ 

2) Log in as admin, click "Authentication" on the left and fill in MDC details
2.1) Skip down to MDC Configuration
2.2) MDC Hostname, Username, Password, map to the Database you setup for MDN. 
2.3) MDC Database is the name of your dev database.

3) Copy includes/functions.php over phpBB3/includes/functions.php

4) Copy viewforum.php over phpBB3/viewforum.php
5) Copy viewtopic.php over phpBB3/viewtopic.php

6) cp -R styles/MDN into phpBB3/styles/
6.1) Admin panel > Styles > Activate MDN and make default for users

Questions?  email fwenzel@mozilla.com
